{"tid":2318284,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"BTS防彈少年團稱霸 tumblr 年度韓團討論榜　BLACKPINK 為名次最高的女團！","createTime":"2020-12-09T08:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T03:19:47.000Z","uid":16659,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"ffd35505363c178414e051cfebd548cbdc0b38e3","tid":2318284,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:32:21.000Z","msg":"2020 年即將來到尾聲，這一年來在海外粉絲愛用的社群 tumblr 上，哪些韓國團體的聲量最高呢？一起來看看前 50 名吧！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\ntumblr 本週公開了年度結算榜，其中的「2020 年最佳韓國團體榜」列出這一年來在社群中獲得最多人討論的團體。首先，第一名毫不意外地由紅遍各地的防彈少年團拿下。<br />\n<br />\n第二名則是出道後不久就在海外引發關注的 Stray Kids，兩者的名次都和去年一樣；今年人氣直線上升的 ATEEZ 一舉上升了 6 個名次，在今年拿下了第三名；第四、五名則是同樣來自於 SM Entertainment 的師兄弟 EXO 和 NCT 127。<br />\n<br />\n離開前五名後，終於出現第一組女團 BLACKPINK，和今年新上榜的 Red Velvet 同為前十名中唯二的女團。而 SEVENTEEN、Monsta X 和 GOT7 也依序拿下第七～九名。<br />\n<br />\n除了上述十團外，TWICE、NCT Dream、本月少女、SHINee、SuperM、MAMAMOO、DAY6、THE BOYZ、Dreamcatcher、ITZY⋯⋯等團也都有上榜，最後就來看看完整名單吧！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_5327d5772970d2eee57a8ddf2d62f767/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-09/132206-888287.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_5327d5772970d2eee57a8ddf2d62f767%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-09%2F132206-888287.png&h=51f09b34&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"70e6b867f56adbddaa524a0098fc7d1633a3a079","tid":2318284,"uid":337986,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:34:28.000Z","msg":"Twice可以收檔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2463c6efd237bb3f166f2bc199b56651f9ad783f","tid":2318284,"uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"70e6b867f56adbddaa524a0098fc7d1633a3a079","tid":2318284,"uid":337986,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:34:28.000Z","msg":"Twice可以收檔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-09T08:35:27.000Z","msg":"Twice永不可收檔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pi